trans-unit.source: Enables Windows authentication with client application services.
trans-unit.target: Windows-verificatie met toepassingsservices client ingeschakeld.

trans-unit.source: You can use client application services to validate users by using Windows authentication.
trans-unit.target: U kunt toepassingsservices client gebruiken om gebruikers te verifiëren met behulp van Windows-verificatie.

trans-unit.source: To enable Windows authentication, you configure your application to use the ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider class.
trans-unit.target: Windows-verificatie inschakelt, moet u uw toepassing gebruik van de klasse ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider configureren.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Configure Client Application Services](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Zie voor meer informatie [hoe: Client toepassingsservices configureren](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: After configuration, you can validate users by calling the `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Na configuratie kunt u gebruikers kunt valideren door het aanroepen van de `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>methode.</xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method internally calls the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: De <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>methode roept intern de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A>methode.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method automatically authenticates the current user and sets the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: De <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>methode automatisch de huidige gebruiker wordt geverifieerd en stelt de `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eigenschap naar een <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>object dat de huidige <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> bevat</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> is configured for your application, you can use the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object to retrieve user role information from the roles service.
trans-unit.target: Als een <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>is geconfigureerd voor uw toepassing, kunt u de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>object voor het ophalen van gebruikersgegevens van de rol van de service rollen.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve a reference to the current ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider instance through the `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: U kunt een verwijzing naar het huidige exemplaar van ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider via ophalen de `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eigenschap.</xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can use the membership provider reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method directly.
trans-unit.target: U kunt de verwijzing van de provider lidmaatschap aan te roepen de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>methode rechtstreeks.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, you will need the membership provider reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A> method, which is not available in the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider> base class.
trans-unit.target: Daarnaast moet u de verwijzing van de provider lidmaatschap naar Roep de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A>methode die niet beschikbaar in de <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider>basis-klasse is.</xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A>

trans-unit.source: Logs out the user.
trans-unit.target: De gebruiker afmelden.

trans-unit.source: For users authenticated through client application services, the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is set to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that enables access to the configured role service.
trans-unit.target: Voor gebruikers worden geverifieerd via toepassingsservices client, de `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eigenschap is ingesteld op een <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>object waarmee toegang tot de geconfigureerde functieservice.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The Logout method resets the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> property to a <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: De methode afmelding stelt de <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>eigenschap naar een <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal>object dat de huidige <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> bevat</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>

trans-unit.source: After you call this method, you can no longer retrieve roles for the user through the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> class.
trans-unit.target: Nadat u deze methode aanroept, kunt u niet meer ophalen rollen voor de gebruiker door de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>klasse.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>

trans-unit.source: To reauthenticate the current user, call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Aanroepen voor het verifiëren van de huidige gebruiker, de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>methode.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The ValidateUser method automatically authenticates the current user and sets the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: De methode ValidateUser automatisch de huidige gebruiker wordt geverifieerd en stelt de `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eigenschap naar een <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>object dat de huidige <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> bevat</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> is configured for your application, you can use the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object to retrieve user role information from the roles service.
trans-unit.target: Als een <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>is geconfigureerd voor uw toepassing, kunt u de <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>object voor het ophalen van gebruikersgegevens van de rol van de service rollen.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>
